{"tid":2199623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Rubio等19位議員聯署去信迪士尼　促解釋《花木蘭》與新彊政府合作細節　羅冠聰：拭目以待","createTime":"2020-09-12T10:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T14:23:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"06759ce80bb9c7e92930b876539db3d132235aab","tid":2199623,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T10:58:57.000Z","msg":"⋯被中共「制裁」的共和黨參議員 Marco Rubio 與 18 位跨黨派議員聯署致函迪士尼，要求他們解釋與新彊政府合作細節。Marco Rubio 在信中質問對方為何明知新疆有拘留營、打壓維吾爾少數族裔的情況，仍然與其合作。信函又提出十個疑問，包括與新疆公安部的合作詳情、迪士尼高層及製作單位在拍攝《花木蘭》前，是否知悉新疆集中營的打壓、為何在新疆人權侵犯問題嚴重情況下，依然選址拍攝，以及共產黨有否參與電影拍攝和決定等。<br />\n<br />\n信函更以迪士尼官網宣言結尾：「社會責任是一項強化競爭力、風險管理、人才流入及保持聲譽的長遠投資。（We believe social responsibility is a long- term investment that serves to strengthen our operations and competitiveness in the marketplace, enhance risk management, attract and engage talented employees, and maintain our reputation.）」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/美參議員聯署去信迪士尼-促解釋-花木蘭-與新彊政府合作細節-羅冠聰-拭目以待/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC-%E4%BF%83%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B-%E8%8A%B1%E6%9C%A8%E8%98%AD-%E8%88%87%E6%96%B0%E5%BD%8A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80-%E7%BE%85%E5%86%A0%E8%81%B0-%E6%8B%AD%E7%9B%AE%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%85%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9fxV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=d7bb9447\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%8E%BB%E4%BF%A1%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC-%E4%BF%83%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B-%E8%8A%B1%E6%9C%A8%E8%98%AD-%E8%88%87%E6%96%B0%E5%BD%8A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80-%E7%BE%85%E5%86%A0%E8%81%B0-%E6%8B%AD%E7%9B%AE%E4%BB%A5%E5%BE%85%2F&h=6292080d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/美參議員聯署去信迪士尼-促解釋-花木蘭-與新彊政府合作細節-羅冠聰-拭目以待/